abstract: International House Hunting column; three-bedroom seaside condominium in Singapore, in 10-year-old Seascape complex in Sentosa Cove, is listed at $5.5 million; market and tips for buying in Singapore highlighted.
lead_paragraph: Singapore was a hot international market, but prices slid after the government imposed restrictions on mortgages and placed additional taxes on purchases by foreigners.
